x last=\"yes\" title=\"Touch Enabled\" icon=\"hand-up\"]All of the sliders are touch enabled so viewers on mobile devices can easily navigate your slides![/content_box]\r\n[/content_boxes]\r\n\r\n[separator top=\"-40\"]\r\n\r\n[content_boxes]\r\n[content_box title=\"Google Maps\" icon=\"map-marker\" ]Goole Maps is fully integrated and users can select custom sizes for the contact page map![/content_box]\r\n[content_box title=\"Social Media\" icon=\"twitter\"]Want your users to stay in touch? Avada has Social Media icons all throughout the theme for you![/content_box]\r\n[content_box title=\"SEO Optimized\" icon=\"search\"]Avada was created with best SEO practices so it allows search engines to index your site content![/content_box]\r\n[content_box last=\"yes\" title=\"Always Improving\" icon=\"signal\"]We love Dagna Music, and so do our customers which is why we constantly add new brands and instruments requested by you.[/content_box]\r\n[/content_boxes]\r\n\r\n[one_half last=\"no\"]\r\n[tagline_box title=\"We know you will love Dagna Music as much as we do. We put so much time and effort into Dagna, and our wonderful customers who buy it. But don\'t take our word for it, see our testimonials from our dedicated customers!\"][/tagline_box]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half last=\"yes\"]\r\n[testimonials]\r\n[testimonial name=\"Sadchidanand Swami\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]Thank you for your very professional and prompt service to help me select my dream guitar! I went to look for answers to my own questions and quickly realized that you had all the answers! In fact everything has been perfect so far. This is by far the most well supported guitar shopping experience I have ever had the pleasure of. Lots of wonderful options. I wished I had found you before I spent money elsewhere. Thanks again for the great support and for a great Epiphone guitar. Much Love and Peace![/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Tushar Chaturvedi,\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]If I could give 100 stars for support and attention to detail I definitely would. I’ve purchased a good number of Electric Guitars from various shops that look good on the outside but after you play them you find numerous problems and very very poor support. I purchased the Aria Electric Guitar and there were a couple of problems too trying to connect it with the right amplifier, but you guys are remarkable – I really mean this. The speed of support and attention to detail is quite phenomenal. If you are considering buying from Dagna at all then take it from me, you will be extremely pleased. Thanks very much to Angad and Paras! [/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Navya Singh\" gender=\"female\" company=\"\"]Excellent Casio Keyboard. One of the best keyboards I have ever used. Every minor detail has been taken care of right from packaging to delivery. Awesome support as well. Not 5 but 10 Star Ratings. [/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Prashant Kumar\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]Amazing Music Instruments Shop and top class support, as I’m a beginner, Angad helped me above and beyond and was more than patient, his responses were quick and he has a genuine care for you to enjoy and move forward with your guitar!.. highly recommended shop and their people! [/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Payal Gupta\" gender=\"female\" company=\"\"]I bought a CTK-1100 Casio Keyboard to start with and I am impressed. Not only the shop is well thought out with good amount options and excellent customisation facilities but their support after sales is exemplary.\r\nI can thoroughly recommend the shop and the manager. I will be buying more stuff![/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Sundeep Ramudamu\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]I have to echo others\' posts, I too can highly recommend this shop for it’s expertise of sales staff and support. Hell I am a designer and have no previous experience with playing guitar, so only use this to build our own new band and am finding it so easy!. To the Dagna Music team – thank you ALL for all the hard work especially when you went through so much trouble to import a Washburn just for me![/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Yogesh Paliwal\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]Hi, I just wanted to say thanks for the great  amplifier. I’m finding new ways to improve it every day and find that it’s been the most user-friendly equipment I’ve ever purchased. I am practically music illiterate and know extremely little if anything at all about mixing, amplification, or any of the inner workings of a mixer. Your recommended set of amplifier and guitar removes all the worry, hassle, frustration and angst that beginners (and novices) feel when playing. If you can listen and follow directions from their sales staff, this shop is for you. I’ve tried a dozen shops and Dagna Music makes almost all of them unnecessary and obsolete.[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Sam Treloar\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]Just wanna say THANK YOU! Dagna Music is just great. It’s easy to find in Dwarka and has some really neat guitar accessories. It’s a pleasure to shop at. My fans are happy and so am I. Go ahead![/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Stephan Vuuren\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\"]Thanks so much for the quick support. You solved my problem. I can’t believe it was such a simple oversight from my side. I misunderstood the instructions, but makes complete sense in hindsight. You rock! Thanks so much for taking the time to help a novice like me. The amplifier is really great and easy to install, even for someone like me who comes predominantly from a DJ background. I’m really impressed with your service and support! [/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Javed Iqbal\" gender=\"male\" company=\"Avada Theme\"]I have to say the shopping experience must be the best I have come across in India, Thanks![/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Gojcus\" gender=\"male\" company=\"Avada Theme\"]Let me say s