0\" button=\"Call Now\" title=\"Dagna Music Shop Electric Acoustic Guitars Delhi\" description=\"The widest range of affordable guitars under one roof!\"][/tagline_box]\r\n\r\n[separator top=\"5\" style=\"double\"]\r\n\r\n[one_half last=\"no\"][testimonials]\r\n[testimonial name=\"BIBHUDUTTA MOHANTY\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\" link=\"http://dagnamusic.com/music-instruments-shop\" target=\"\"]\"Great Service and quality of product. Really nice experience and first service with right price.\"[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Shobhana Sukriti \" gender=\"female\" company=\"\" link=\"http://dagnamusic.com/music-instruments-shop\" target=\"\"]\" It was a pleasant experience to buy the guitar...As promised, it was promptly delivered the next day. The guitar came in excellent condition. Thank you very much to Angad &amp; Paras!\"[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Janardan Mahadevan\" gender=\"male\" company=\"\" link=\"http://dagnamusic.com/music-instruments-shop\" target=\"\"]\"Good value for money instrument for a beginner. Nice instrument - I bought a i433 also from Mozart Singh-, both these are good value for money. More importantly, I find Mozart Singh to be a knowledgeable, trustworthy seller who listens to your requirements and helps you decide. Excellent follow through on our purchases to ensure a smooth delivery. Highly <span class=\"il\">recommended</span>.\"[/testimonial]\r\n\r\n[testimonial name=\"Sam Treloar \" gender=\"male\" company=\"\" link=\"http://dagnamusic.com/music-instruments-shop\" target=\"\"]\"My first Casio was a CTK-601 that I bought in 2001. I found it really hard to program, so I just used it for what I got it for - adding depth to my recording which were mostly based around guitar. This one is still hard to get my head around (I am an \'older citizen\', 58yo) , so I\'ll probably do much the same thing with it.\r\nThe other main glaring negative is the lack of facility for swell pedal. Of course the great drawbar sounds don\'t have touch sensitivity, but apart from the General Midi organs, the AHL organ presets have very little variance to touch pressure despite the touch response settings already set to the max. Without the swell or volume pedal, this makes the otherwise excellent organ sounds a bit machine-like and robotic. Apart from that, the 7300IN represents value for money, especially with the fine tune temperament capabilities necessary for authentic Indian instrument sounds. If you\'re just looking to create Bollywood style you\'ll be happy as no keyboard can really duplicate the real thing.\r\nOn the positive side, I really really like the number 1 piano sound. Coupled with Kirnberger or Werkmeister temperament, it is very sweet with the slightly flatter thirds combining beautifully with the smooth grand piano sound. I am looking forward to making some nice recordings now, the overall sound is a vast improvement on my previous, and the sounds that haven\'t changed has its benefits because I can reproduce faithfully the same sounds as on my earlier CD\'s.\r\nSumming up, great sounds at a bargain price but not a user-friendly interface for programming - my guess is that that part was designed by a nerd, not a musician ;-)\"[/testimonial]\r\n[/testimonials]\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half last=\"yes\"]\r\n<h2>What Else? Over 21,000 Users Choose Dagna!</h2>\r\n[separator top=\"30\" style=\"single\"]\r\nDagna has over <strong><span style=\"color: #84b231;\">100 Brands of Acoustic and Electric Guitars!</span></strong> <strong>Famous Brands like</strong><span style=\"color: #84b231;\"><strong> Yamaha, Aria, Epiphone, Walden, Ibanez, Ashton, Washburn</strong></span><span style=\"color: #84b231;\"><strong> and more</strong></span>, along with the spectrum of affordable brands! We are musicians and music teachers and put <strong><span style=\"color: #84b231;\">lots of love</span></strong> into this endeavor and have stocked something for everyone!\r\n[separator top=\"28\"]\r\n[checklist